verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
PrFont34Bin0BinSub0Frac0Def1Margin0Margin0Jc1Indent1440Lim0Lim1The battle is won by lifting Jesus
Higher in the midst of thee.
Joy, joy, joy is the victory.
The battle is won by lifting Jesus
Higher in the midst of thee.
Sing and shout the victory.
CHORUS:
Let us sing, sing for joy.
Sing, sing for joy
Sing, sing for joy,
Sing for joy to the Lord all the earth.
